Clockwork can be made on a Crafting table 2 or better in the Workshop of a Player-owned house. A Clockwork requires a steel bar and level 8 Crafting to make and gives 15 Crafting experience.

The clockwork mechanism is a key component in the following:

  • Toy soldier
  • Toy doll
  • Clockwork penguin
  • Clockwork mice
  • Clockwork cat
  • Oak, Teak, and Gilded clocks.
  • Trapdoor
  • Watch
  • Bird house
